Connections to ESP32
LORA RFM95W

    3.3V --> 3.3V
    GND --> GND
    RESET --> 14
    NSS --> 5
    SCK --> 18
    MOSI --> 23
    MISO --> 19

OLED

    VCC --> 3.3V
    GND --> GND
    SCL --> 21
    SDA --> 22

Joystick

    VCC --> 3.3V
    GND --> GND
    X --> 35
    Y --> 34

Button 1

    GND
    D12

Button 2

    GND
    D13

TP4056

    + --> Vin (place a switch between TP4056 + and Vin)
    - --> GND
    B+ --> Battery +
    B- --> Battery -
